            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Tess, what do you think about this...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Give me a second... I'll taste it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It's sweet and delicious!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That's good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "You're amazing Sophie. It's really sweet! I'd want to put this on bread and eat it every day!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Um, that wouldn't be good... I mean, it's medicine, after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But I think your little brothers wouldn't mind taking this medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, no doubt about that. In fact, they'd probably want seconds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha, just don't let them have that. Drinking too much medicine is poisonous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I know that. I'm just saying how good your medicine is, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Thanks for this, I mean it. You made something like this for my little brothers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's fine, you're always helping me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha, you're such a good girl. Maybe I should treat you to something nice."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Wow, really?! Yay!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Of course! Anyway, come back to the shop anytime."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I will!"
        }
    ]
